# Git configuration for MATLAB/Simulink
# To view changes in Simulink models, use the following terminal command:
# git difftool -t mlDiff -- <file_path.slx>

# Mark Simulink models as binary and enable merge/diff tools
*.slx binary merge=mlAutoMerge
*.mdl binary merge=mlAutoMerge

# Mark test data files as binary
*.mldatx binary